tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE SoilSamples (
  sample_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  pH_level FLOAT,
  moisture_content FLOAT,
  nutrient_levels JSON,
  sample_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE soil_samples (
    sample_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(100),
    pH_level FLOAT,
    moisture_content FLOAT,
    nutrient_levels JSON
);
